{"tid":875544,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人係有兩個mode: (1)擴散  (2)專注","createTime":"2018-10-25T03:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T04:27:51.000Z","uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9a1e39f3023ffd96870813e94f7b1b1561b970fd","tid":875544,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"專注mode 係for 你睇得好details <br />\n擴散mode 係for 你睇到big picture <br />\n<br />\n一般人冇留意自己有呢兩個mode <br />\n唔會特意去switch between 呢兩個mode <br />\n即: 識專注既人, 會過份咁用專注mode <br />\n識擴散既人, 會過份咁用擴散mode<br />\n<br />\n過份咁專注既人, 好易會變成毒撚, 活係自己世界<br />\n過份咁擴散既人, 好易會變成mk , 好鍾意吹水 <br />\n<br />\n物極必反, 係永恆既道理 <br />\n所以學習係專注及擴散間轉換, 能受惠終生<br />\n<br />\n大家專心小小聽住, 以下係重點<br />\n擴散mode 只有一個情況下有用, <br />\n就係專注mode咁吸收大量知識後, <br />\n再擴散去睇big picture <br />\n咁先會有實際而唔係mk 9upper 咁吹水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而識得係呢兩個mode 之間轉換 <br />\n就係我, 大佬彪"},{"pid":"4631aad8c05d98d1b2d1b3a4726e60dc1ae95961","tid":875544,"uid":189053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ddc473fde9a76db360f21b973970cecc47172661","tid":875544,"uid":187108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"即係您精神錯亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3d8a90903523b13cf3713aed8e6435c8b08d89","tid":875544,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4631aad8c05d98d1b2d1b3a4726e60dc1ae95961","tid":875544,"uid":189053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:26:07.000Z","msg":"唔清楚咩係coursera"},{"pid":"19ac25bd5430daddc6df04f6ba508c3699cb48d1","tid":875544,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc473fde9a76db360f21b973970cecc47172661","tid":875544,"uid":187108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"即係您精神錯亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ecf86cae0be15c36adc6d656833b3a109bcd54","tid":875544,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"我仲有料<br />\n想知我再講"},{"pid":"2192de9a18750e4c43273098a321175035554984","tid":875544,"uid":7519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"Thinking fast and slow?"},{"pid":"d10f4ed71c637e02b47b8b69ff0135e161219b13","tid":875544,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2192de9a18750e4c43273098a321175035554984","tid":875544,"uid":7519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"Thinking fast and slow?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:30:52.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"9d75645cabed787e4bd0bf7d913b07d9de3d0123","tid":875544,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:38:10.000Z","msg":"冇人想知就算"},{"pid":"4c19a47f28c2c11eaa60a7cc37cc425ced8d244b","tid":875544,"uid":204943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3ecf86cae0be15c36adc6d656833b3a109bcd54","tid":875544,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"我仲有料<br />\n想知我再講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a47233a08edef85b31d0bee185d1d2d03eee68e","tid":875544,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:56:58.000Z","msg":"想講再知"},{"pid":"7a246d00963b3d1c8c466dfebc39af507e48e642","tid":875544,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:58:19.000Z","msg":"最尾果句笑左"},{"pid":"eb34765c10b30af7dcc4994349167374cff2811d","tid":875544,"uid":163554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T04:07:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cbb9dc4ec854d1cd1b014fa82930cd348210735","tid":875544,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c19a47f28c2c11eaa60a7cc37cc425ced8d244b","tid":875544,"uid":204943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3ecf86cae0be15c36adc6d656833b3a109bcd54","tid":875544,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"我仲有料<br />\n想知我再講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T04:17:47.000Z","msg":"黎到最重要既一環：如何實際轉換呢兩種mode ? <br />\n要專注mode 啟動, 有好多方法<br />\n舉少少例子俾大家試下：<br />\n1）Set 時間限制, 迫使自己指定時間內完成某種專注活動<br />\n2）清晨日照時工作 <br />\n3）飲少量茶，建議綠茶<br />\n4）運動<br />\n<br />\n而擴散既方法，亦有好多，例如：<br />\n1）晚上燈光昏暗時與人交談<br />\n2）散步時思考<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">（當年蘇格拉底好鍾意同學生邊散步，邊探討哲學問題）</span></em><br />\n3）出門去旅行，去新奇未體驗過既地方<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><em>（周星馳曾經講過，好多抵死有趣既劇本情節，都係出門旅行時諗到）</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謹記物極必反<br />\n好多歷史上舉世既Idea <br />\n都係於人類處於擴散性思維中誕生<br />\n而呢堆出色既人類，平日係充滿住專注性既工作<br />\n希望大家活用腦部 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大佬彪上<br />\n2018年10月25日"},{"pid":"34ffb2d9b9aa3e5c23c69a32b2ada6a0f2f43796","tid":875544,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T04:19:26.000Z","msg":"懶係野咁"},{"pid":"4ec9251ba9d6f02dbcf677e7c2bb3cb198a5aa95","tid":875544,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34ffb2d9b9aa3e5c23c69a32b2ada6a0f2f43796","tid":875544,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T04:19:26.000Z","msg":"懶係野咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"智商30"},{"pid":"17c432319bb05b1e64f779e21f920a21e27aa0a2","tid":875544,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T04:27:51.000Z","msg":"認真Post 冇人理？<br />\n睇黎我都係適合做KOL 多d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}